--[[ ROBBERY SCANNER â€” server-hopping scout (detection only; main autorob reads the report)

  Runs ONLY on accounts whose username contains "RobberyScanner". Crawls servers; on each one
  scans robberies, reports the open ones (with an absolute despawn time + a join link), then hops.

  SHARED BRAIN: scouts coordinate through CONFIG.BrainUrl (a read/write JSON endpoint). Each scout
    avoids servers already VISITED or CLAIMED by another scout, so they don't pile into one server.

  DESPAWN THROUGH TIME ALONE: despawnAt / ePromptsAt are absolute UNIX timestamps. Discord renders
    them as <t:..:R> (live, self-updating). The autorob reads despawnAt and does despawnAt - os.time().

  STREAMING: on join the plane crates + onboard players are unloaded; we point the camera at the
    plane and RequestStreamAround it, then wait for the crate count to stabilise before reporting.

  SELF-EXECUTE: drop in the Potassium autoexec folder. Halt with a robscan_stop.txt in the workspace.
  SET: CONFIG.BotUrl + CONFIG.RobberyToken (the Discord bot's /robbery endpoint + shared secret).
]]

